        <mxCell id="fwrules" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef9e7;strokeColor=#b7950b;align=left;spacing=8;fontSize=10" value="&lt;b&gt;POLICY FIREWALL — zona VOICE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• VOICE → WAN: allow SIP/RTP/HTTPS/NTP/DNS&lt;br&gt;• VOICE ↔ LAN1: &lt;b&gt;deny&lt;/b&gt; (eccetto gestione)&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;SIP ALG / transformation: OFF&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;PoE&lt;/b&gt;: GS2220 HP, budget 375 W/switch&lt;br&gt;Porte telefoni → PoE priority &lt;b&gt;High/Critical&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Verificare UPS su entrambi i piani" vertex="1">
